Statement of Purpose

The Commons Against Empire and Capital Zero 1.0 Universal instrument, or CAEC0 1.0 Universal, is intended to waive, abandon, or otherwise relinquish, to the fullest extent permitted by law, copyright and related rights in the Work identified with this instrument, so that the Work may be freely used, reproduced, modified, distributed, and shared by anyone for any purpose, subject only to limits that cannot lawfully be waived.

No Trademark or Endorsement Rights

This instrument does not grant trademark rights, publicity rights, privacy rights, or any right to imply endorsement, sponsorship, or affiliation.

No Warranties

The Work is provided as-is and without warranties of any kind, to the fullest extent permitted by law.

Scope

This file applies only to the repository contents identified by the project as being released under CAEC0 1.0 Universal. It does not by itself alter the license terms of any separate deed, legal code, or other licensing instrument published by this repository.
